&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the customer journey from end to end, whether it’s first discovery call, demoing, running pilots or negotiation and closing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-thread opportunities to cultivate champions and loop in decision makers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relay customer needs to our product team, to drive our product roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine your craft and sharing best practices with your teammates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and communicating different ways we can improve our process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forecast with accuracy to ensure we’re focusing on the right customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we value:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Being customer-obsessed&lt;/strong&gt;: You’ll need to get to your goals the right way, as we’d rather lose a deal than mislead customers. We expect all of our customer facing team to excel at responsiveness, understanding customer needs and having the product knowledge to solve customer problems.&lt;/li&gt;
